description.en: Baby Pancake is a automatic yield generating token that launched fairly on the BSC on 29/7/2021. Holders of at least 200,000 $BPCake tokens will automatically receive $Cake tokens airdropped into their wallets every hour. It is a divided yield paying token that rewards holders just for holding. The project was launched on the BSC due to the fast transactions and low fees. A clear roadmap was set up and is being followed to ensure the success of the token.
